<ol class="max-w-lg space-y-1 text-gray-500 list-decimal list-inside dark:text-gray-400">
    <li>
        <span>After creating the Access, the driver will receive an<span class="font-medium text-gray-600 dark:text-white"> SMS containing the access link</span> for the parking lot.</span>
    </li>
    <li>
        <span>The driver must click the <span class="font-medium text-gray-600 dark:text-white">access link</span> contained in the SMS.</span>
    </li>
    <li>
        <span>After clicking the link they will be redirected to a <span class="font-medium text-gray-600 dark:text-white">web qrcode scanner </span> where they are to scan the Qrcode at the parking lot assigned to them.</span>
    </li>
    <li>
        <span>After <span class="font-medium text-gray-600 dark:text-white">successfully scanning</span> the Qrcode, the access will be <span class="font-medium text-gray-600 dark:text-white">activated</span> and they will be logged in to their dashboard.</span>
    </li>
</ol>
